 Scheme
==============================

 CLI YAML
  |   |
  |   |
  |   |           Output
  |   |
  |   |	           ^  ^ 
  |   |            |  |
  V   V   +--------+  |
          |           |
Configuration -->  Run  <-- StepDefinitions
  |
  |                ^  ^
  |                |  |
  |     +----------+  +-----------+
  |	    |      	                  |
  | Reporter                  Scenarios <-- Grammar <-- Languages
  |                                                        
  |                                                        ^
  |                                                        |
  +--------------------------------------------------------+


 Options
==============================
  tags, scenario, exclude => Run (loading features)
  autoformat, dry-run => Run (dry run, reporter choosing)
  strict => Run
  language => Language 
  format => Run (for choose Reporter(s))
  require, guess => StepDefinitions
  out => Output (where)
  profile => Configuration
  [no-]color, no-source, no-snippets, quiet, verbose, no-multiline => Reporter 

